<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.7">
<l>niṟuttinu muḷḷattuk koḷḷun teyvaṅka ḷummaiyuy yakkoḷ</l>
<l>maṟuttu mavaṉōṭē kaṇṭīr mārkkaṇ ṭēyaṉuṅ kariyē</l>
<l>kaṟutta maṉamoṉṟum vēṇṭā kaṇṇaṉal lālteyva millai</l>
<l>iṟuppatel lāmavaṉ mūrtti yāyavark kēyi ṟumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See together with him, who refuses to accept, in order to save you, the gods</l>
<l>that set up themselves [and] take your hearts, also Mārkaṇḍeya as witness.</l>
<l>There is not god except Kṛṣṇa who does not want anything in [his] keen mind.</l>
<l>All that stays is his form. Stay for those whom he becomes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
